name: Hawa Cat Soaks in Paris
description:
Hawa Cat is soaking in the atmosphere of the great writers, artists, dancers, musicians & poets who always flocked to Paris to sit and talk at the Cafe De Flor. 

That was the last golden age which led to Impressionism art, Romantic art, Expressionism, Futurism, cubism, Abstract art, and finally Conceptual Art with Marcel Duchamp’s “Ready Made’.

Hawa Cat  doesn’t know anyone in Paris and, besides,  is very short on cash. In any case, there is no one here because they are all at home making NFTs & talking  on Twitter Spaces. She is so excited because this NFT art renaissance is even better than the European one which she had always dreamed of. This new golden age includes everyone from all over the world who owns a phone and excludes the business model of the  ‘starving artist’ which ruined many masterpieces.
